{"tid":1529431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"請查正! 有自稱美聯社記者, 懷疑向黑警通信報信, 報告示威者位置.","createTime":"2019-09-01T17:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:39.000Z","uid":192781,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"41b5e983bbba01ec52156b1239e793c74f2bf0b1","tid":1529431,"uid":192781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:34:05.000Z","msg":"此人自稱美聯社記者, 但由831之前到依家, 從未見過此人.<br />\n相比起路透社呢尐世界大嘅通訊社, 螢光衫同頭罩都打晒路透社, 此人裝備非簡陋;<br />\n亦有人話佢係政府新聞處記者.<br />\n懷疑此人向黑警通風報信, 報告示威者位置, 希望大家小心此人及查正此人.<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ME35PUd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FME35PUd.jpg&h=eca53e50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/czpTYNy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FczpTYNy.jpg&h=29cad476&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mz3agze.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMz3agze.jpg&h=1f067c41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a3e530aa6790f255035ad1c3a136763c46a59eaf","tid":1529431,"uid":276758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"成個許紹雄咁"},{"pid":"f9b603fdcf2adaa5d13e7f1df38ae3d14658c7a5","tid":1529431,"uid":119864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"推一推先"},{"pid":"79ddae0be4af059dc728e30b6122d8578f4d3ffc","tid":1529431,"uid":118330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:39:59.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0874af53d2a1e2369564b00e5cb4be0df1fe69c5","tid":1529431,"uid":72800,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:40:26.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">暗黑兵法劇本 出沒注意：</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">沒收gear 未來兩星期大量武警喬裝示威者</span></span>嫁禍衝擊<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>內部分化</strong></span>示威者、<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">酷刑凌虐威嚇</span></span></strong>被捕人士、<br />\n邊緣打壓香港 渲染港獨<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">阻抗爭之風蔓延內陸</span></strong>、<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: green;\">暴力鎮壓 拘捕 扣留 私刑</span></strong>企圖瓦解前線、<br />\n文宣<strong><span style=\"color: violet;\">抹黑 嫁禍 插贜</span></strong>示威者、<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">暗殺</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第一滴血</span> 逆轉民意 國際譴責、<br />\n市民絕望噤聲 憤怒冷卻、<br />\n中立派 賺錢派 <strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">政治疲勞</span></strong>、<br />\n鼓吹經濟下滑風向 富豪商家屈服 加速瓦解、<br />\n學季始開，拖延 分散 擊破、<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">白色恐怖、清除異己、染紅香港</span></strong></span><br />\n拖字訣 雨傘結局 ⋯<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大追捕 清算開始</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"eff43fb43fba80e20906092503cfd4139d0a8b1e","tid":1529431,"uid":240319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:41:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"45730d6ff2c5708267fc9b3093f8ee0ede1dc530","tid":1529431,"uid":167878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:42:34.000Z","msg":"藍絲樣"},{"pid":"177109f8fd69a4764c15e5034988d2ffc624a8f7","tid":1529431,"uid":308226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3e530aa6790f255035ad1c3a136763c46a59eaf","tid":1529431,"uid":276758,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:35:01.000Z","msg":"成個許紹雄咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:43:21.000Z","msg":"佢似比目魚 許紹雄得意好多"},{"pid":"3d0047277db47bcc6342b1dbce55c9c849eb47e6","tid":1529431,"uid":264706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:45:44.000Z","msg":"無認錯的話佢係Vincent Yu<br />\n資深記者<br />\n深黃<br />\n<br />\n你地可以check 下佢之前跟過的新聞或展覽"},{"pid":"93663cfc7162335fba2e946a7e087da9c74c69e5","tid":1529431,"uid":264706,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T17:55:12.000Z","msg":"講多少少<br />\n佢已經係神台級數<br />\n平時唔駛成日上前線<br />\